data.description: Welcome to your dream home in the heart of North Port! This 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom pool home is nestled along a picturesque canal, offering the perfect blend of relaxation and outdoor living. As you enter, you'll be greeted by an open and airy living space with abundant natural light that showcases the inviting pool and water views. The spacious living room features vaulted ceilings and flows seamlessly into the dining area and kitchen, creating an ideal space for entertaining family and friends. Cooking enthusiasts will love preparing meals in the kitchen that features Corian countertops, a large breakfast bar, crown molding, a glass top stove, tiled backsplash, and a double door pantry. The master bedroom is a true retreat, complete with a large window surrounded by a custom built-in bookcase that shows gorgeous views of the pool and backyard canal. Wake up to beautiful water views, and unwind in the custom en-suite bathroom with a roman shower and dual walk-in closets. Two additional bedrooms provide ample space for guests or a growing family, and a second full bathroom ensures everyone's comfort. Step outside to your private oasis and take a dip in the sparkling pool, perfect for cooling off on hot Florida days. Enjoy your morning coffee on the patio while watching the wildlife along the canal. The oversized, fenced backyard offers direct access to the water, making it an ideal spot for kayaking, fishing, or simply relaxing by the water's edge. Lush landscaping enhances the property's curb appeal with mature trees, plants, shrubs, oak & palm trees. Additional features of this home include a a new roof, septic, A/C, water system, hurricane windows, washer and dryer. The sellers have contracted a new fence to go around the pool. This home is located in a quiet and friendly neighborhood, you'll have easy access to shopping, dining, parks, and golf courses. North Port is known for its natural beauty and outdoor recreational opportunities, making it a fantastic place to call home. Don't miss the opportunity to own this waterfront gem. Schedule a showing today and make your Florida dream a reality!
